SUBDIRECTORY: manuals

This directory contains various other subdirectories,
each of which contains an example used in the user documentation.

A very basic occam program and configuration can be found in `simple'.
A more complex fully worked example can be found in `sorter'.

advconf		Advanced use of the configurer
assert		Asserting subsystem analyse and reset
config		Some configurer examples using IF
dynamic		Dynamic code loading examples from Low Level Programming
idebug		Worked examples using the idebug debugger
simple		The simple example from Getting Started
sorter		The sorter example; for single and multiple processors
mixed		Mixed language examples
mux		Multiplexor example from Host Services chapter
userboot	User bootstraps
